# v1 Baseline Behaviour Map

## Fantail (Fish / A)
- Signature: sprint-rest cycles, edge-check pauses
- Telemetry tells: high pause_ratio, higher speed std, balanced zone spread
- Role: scout / pulse mover / reset-return

## Kiwi (Ant_fast / B)
- Signature: load-tolerant exploration, low pause, ground persistence
- Telemetry tells: low pause_ratio, steady speed, heavy Transition/Library time
- Role: forager / stubborn continuity / slow-burn learning

## Kiwi (Ant_slow / C)
- Signature: same as kiwi but “low gear”, more linger
- Telemetry tells: lower avg_speed, fewer transitions
- Role: stabilizer / drift anchor / patience agent

## Sparrow (Bird / D)
- Signature: wide looping turns, lighter commitment, occasional perch
- Telemetry tells: moderate speed variance, low-to-mid pause_ratio, fast scanning transitions
- Role: surveyor / pattern-sampler / overview agent
